      "endS": 17.6,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Click System Alerts.",
      "startS": 18,
      "endS": 19.239,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "One rule before anything else.",
      "startS": 20.042,
      "endS": 22.023,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "Reach this page through the sidebar, never by typing its address.",
      "startS": 22.423,
      "endS": 25.846,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "The direct U-R-L still answers four oh four, while this link renders everything.",
      "startS": 26.237,
      "endS": 30.939,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "The page settles inside the shell, breadcrumb up top,",
      "startS": 31.442,
      "endS": 34.25,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "and four K-P-I tiles waiting across the band.",
      "startS": 34.616,
      "endS": 37.36,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Read the band left to right.",
      "startS": 37.76,
      "endS": 39.554,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Three alerts open right now.",
      "startS": 40.795,
      "endS": 42.303,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Fourteen logged today.",
      "startS": 42.659,
      "endS": 44.028,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "And of the open three, one critical against two warnings.",
      "startS": 44.398,
      "endS": 47.743,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "That single critical is the number that decides whether your coffee waits.",
      "startS": 47.947,
      "endS": 51.98,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Everything below this band exists to explain these four tiles.",
      "startS": 52.423,
      "endS": 56.163,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Upper left, Alert Volume.",
      "startS": 56.56,
      "endS": 58.464,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "A year of history on one line, January through December,",
      "startS": 58.958,
      "endS": 62.397,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "one hundred forty eight alerts in all and trending down eight percent.",
      "startS": 62.675,
      "endS": 66.591,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "That slope is the long view.",
      "startS": 66.982,
      "endS": 68.834,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "It is the sentence a quarterly health review wants to write.",
      "startS": 69.132,
      "endS": 72.131,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Next panel, By Severity.",
