      "endS": 74.456,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Four levels.",
      "startS": 74.859,
      "endS": 75.662,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Info carries fifty eight percent of the traffic, warnings twenty eight,",
      "startS": 76.147,
      "endS": 79.982,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "errors ten, critical just four.",
      "startS": 80.25,
      "endS": 82.684,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Most of what this feed says is routine noise.",
      "startS": 83.27,
      "endS": 85.782,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Which is exactly why a critical row deserves your full attention when one shows up.",
      "startS": 86.203,
      "endS": 90.56,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Then System Health.",
      "startS": 90.96,
      "endS": 92.227,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "Eighty six percent healthy, ten warning, four critical.",
      "startS": 92.969,
      "endS": 96.463,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Hold on that four.",
      "startS": 97.096,
      "endS": 98.067,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "It matches the critical slice next door, one fact drawn two ways.",
      "startS": 98.48,
      "endS": 102.439,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "When two panels agree like that, you can trust the read.",
      "startS": 102.95,
      "endS": 105.734,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Scroll to the Alert List.",
      "startS": 106.16,
      "endS": 107.712,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "Six columns carry each alert's story:",
      "startS": 108.499,
      "endS": 110.846,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "when it fired, what kind, how severe, which site, what it said, and whether it is still open.",
      "startS": 111.366,
      "endS": 113.209,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Two buttons above the table stay untouched.",
